00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:16.329
the blood debts you owe?

00:02:17.560 --> 00:02:18.360
Zhou Guannan.

00:02:19.480 --> 00:02:21.079
It's time for all this to end.

00:02:29.520 --> 00:02:31.450
You actually had a dream like this.

00:02:31.760 --> 00:02:33.290
You're scared, aren't you?

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:36.600
Why would I be scared?

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:40.200
From the day I was left all alone,

00:02:40.480 --> 00:02:42.440
I have had nothing to fear.

00:02:43.400 --> 00:02:44.400
But you know

00:02:44.840 --> 00:02:47.300
they will catch you themselves eventually.

00:02:49.480 --> 00:02:50.740
Have you ever wondered

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:53.040
if what you are doing

00:02:54.160 --> 00:02:55.640
has truly fulfilled the meaning

00:02:55.640 --> 00:02:56.920
you are searching for?

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:51.880
Zhang Wendong

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:52.730
has escaped.

00:03:53.800 --> 00:03:54.800
Find him quickly.

00:03:54.800 --> 00:03:56.329
Zhang Wendong is in danger.

00:03:59.440 --> 00:04:00.040
Contact the traffic police

00:04:00.040 --> 00:04:00.880
to lock down and search.

00:04:00.880 --> 00:04:01.810
We must find him.

00:04:06.360 --> 00:04:08.000
Tell me what time the boat arrives.

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:09.000
Hurry, hurry.

00:04:11.200 --> 00:04:11.760
Useless.

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:33.360
Zhou Guannan.

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:36.620
What are you doing?

00:04:41.240 --> 00:04:41.770
Guannan.

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:44.980
What's wrong with you?

00:04:45.320 --> 00:04:46.450
Have you forgotten?

00:04:46.480 --> 00:04:47.520
When you were in school,

00:04:47.520 --> 00:04:49.000
your teacher was so good to you.

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:49.720
Have you forgotten how much effort

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:51.320
was put into your education?

00:04:51.760 --> 00:04:53.960
You can't treat your teacher like this.

00:04:54.600 --> 00:04:55.360
I know.

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:57.680
Are you in some kind of trouble?

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:58.940
Are you short on money?

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:00.440
If you needed it, you could've told me.

00:05:00.440 --> 00:05:01.700
I could've helped you.

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:02.840
No matter how much you want,

00:05:02.840 --> 00:05:03.900
I can give it to you.

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:06.050
I can satisfy all your needs, you know?

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:10.440
Calm down.

00:05:11.760 --> 00:05:12.320
Guannan,

00:05:12.880 --> 00:05:13.680
